          <span class="country-title"><%= country.name.titleize.gsub("-", " ") %></span>
          <div class=legality-status><%= show_svg('green-check.svg')%> Legal</div>
          </h3>
<div class="legal-description">
  <p>Thailand deems the trading and holding of bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies legal, lifting a previous ban the Thai Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) enacted in 2014.</p>
